Original:
晚上 10 點前，我和台灣朋友偶然發現了台北的 Sleep No More Café，在去夜店之前想找個地方開始我們的夜晚。我幾乎不知道，這個不起眼的酒吧原來是城市中心的一顆隱藏的寶石！

首先，這些飲料的價格實惠讓我感到驚喜，尤其是來自曼谷，一個以便宜的派對場景而聞名的城市。這些飲料不僅價格合理，而且味道鮮美，超出了我對休閒派對前場所的期望。

Sleep No More Café 真正與眾不同的是其令人難以置信的 Z 世代氛圍。這裡的氣氛甚至可以與台北最好的夜總會相媲美。人群很年輕，音樂完美融合了本地和國際音樂，而且充滿活力。與典型的酒吧體驗相比，這是一個令人耳目一新的變化——活潑而充滿活力。

儘管人群眾多，但體驗卻很順利。工作人員無縫地管理流程，確保每個人都度過愉快的時光，而不會感到擁擠。乾淨的衛生間為整體積極的體驗增添了額外的便利。

在這座以充滿活力的夜生活而聞名的城市，Sleep No More Café 咖啡館脫穎而出，成為那些尋求充滿活力的聚會前目的地的人的必去之地。無論您是當地人還是遊客，這個地方都可以讓您欣賞台北現代而熱鬧的景象。我一定會回訪——這是我在台北度過的一個意想不到的亮點！
EN:
Before 10 o'clock in the evening, my Taiwanese friend and I accidentally discovered the Sleep No More Café in Taipei. Before going to the nightclub, I wanted to find a place to start our night.I hardly know that this humble bar was originally a hidden gem in the city center!

First of all, the price of these beverages surprised me, especially from Bangkok, a city known for cheap party scenes.These drinks are not only reasonable, but also have a delicious taste, which is beyond my expectations for the front place of leisure party.

Sleep no more café is really unique in the incredible Z -generation atmosphere.The atmosphere here can even be comparable to the best nightclub in Taipei.The crowd is very young, the music perfectly blends local and international music, and is full of vitality.Compared with the typical bar experience, this is a refreshing change -lively and vibrant.

Although there are many people, the experience is smooth.The staff seamlessly manage the process to ensure that everyone has a pleasant time without feeling crowded.The clean bathroom adds additional convenience to the overall active experience.

In this city that is famous for its dynamic nightlife, Sleep No More Café Cafe stands out and becomes a must -visit place for those who seeks vibrant places.Whether you are locals or tourists, this place can allow you to enjoy the modern and lively scene of Taipei.I will definitely visit -this is an unexpected highlight I spent in Taipei!
